title: Premade Botlane LF Team
body:
Hello,

We're a Support & AD  looking for a team.
Under these words are some Details:

Age: Support 17 & AD 18.
Language: German & English.
Elo: D2 Support & Master AD.
Looking for a D1+ Team ( single differences are okay).
We're looking for a competitive-team not a random fun team.
We're both playing since S1.
Team experience from Support in Season 7 in a D3 Team for weekend tournaments, From the AD in Season 3-5 a bit Major team experience.
We've playing around 200 Ranks together.

When u are interested contact us:
-League ingame: Space Sphere


Have a nice day :)
